description: Nineteen people have been confirmed dead and around 50 injured after a terrorist attack inside Manchester Arena at the end of a teen concert tonight.
title: BREAKING NEWS: Emergency services rush to Manchester Arena

author: By Shyam Dodge For Dailymail.com
description: Celebrities have begun paying tribute to victims of terrifying explosions inside Manchester Arena on Monday night. Several people were killed after explosions were heard inside the venue.
title: Celebrities pray for victims of Manchester Arena explosions

author: By Thomas Burrows, Lucy-Mae Beers and Daniel Peters For Mailonline
description: Panicked parents are using social media to try and locate their children after 19 people were killed and 50 injured when explosions went off at Manchester Arena.
title: Parents turn to Facebook to find kids after Manchester Arena explosion

author: Euan McKirdy, Zayn Nabbi, Samantha Beech and Darran Simon, CNN
description: At least 19 people are dead and almost 60 injured in what police are treating as a terrorist incident Monday night at Manchester Arena, where pop singer Ariana Grande was performing.
title: Manchester Arena explosion: 19 dead after blast at Ariana Grande concert

author: Tom Batchelor
description: Nineteen people have died at Manchester Arena following a reported explosion at an Ariana Grande concert, police have said. Theresa May has said it is being treated as "an appalling terrorist attack", and suspended all election campaigning in its wake. Footage taken inside the arena has shown thousands of panicked young people fleeing the arena covered in blood and crying.
title: 19 confirmed dead and 50 injured after reported explosion at Manchester Arena – live updates

description: Witnesses recount the chaotic scenes following a deadly incident at Manchester Arena.
title: 'I've never felt so scared in my life': Witnesses describe concert mayhem
